snippet.title: Rōnin Trail Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Rōnin Trail is an open-world adventure game about a wandering samurai searching for his purpose. You play as a survivor of war who must take on odd jobs and bounties to make a living.

KS: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ronintrail/ronin-trail
Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1606970/Ronin_Trail/
